{"tid":1377772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊嚟為我哋嘅健康加油","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T14:46:07.000Z","uid":219940,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4ec07c48de74c5fd3110921e31499d474f1327","tid":1377772,"uid":219940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"踏入社會之後 <br />\n發現自己個個禮拜坐office <br />\n運動量相比起以前真係少咗太多<br />\n<br />\n為咗解決健康煩惱，我最近開始打網球<br />\n想向大家推薦一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n網球運動作為隔網的健身運動項目，對增進人的體質、愉悅身心、發展智力、培養頑強意志品質具有良好的作用。<br />\n<br />\n由於各項身體機經常得到鍛煉，人體長期處於一個積極的、良性發展狀態，這對控制體重，減少心血管疾病、預防骨質疏鬆、延緩衰老、保持生命活力等都有良好的作用。<br />\n<br />\n星期一至五好忙要OT不了？<br />\n咁咪星期六日打囉<br />\n為咗健康，運動一定要多做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/9jjgqz5.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhealth%2F9jjgqz5.amp&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=c17cb9a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/9jjgqz5.amp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4786ccf0e8a8b69c4dc599bc0a4f476fd4201b61","tid":1377772,"uid":38237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:37:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n要光復香港，大家一齊手動罷工啦！！！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打爆啲交通燈會唔會易過全民死火燈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1377458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1377458</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"613eb7d0625ada67b56844c9bb100cc4b9f3e732","tid":1377772,"uid":219940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4786ccf0e8a8b69c4dc599bc0a4f476fd4201b61","tid":137